); Western Indian Ocean: Madagascar (
<bibRefCitation author="Ledoyer M." box="[199,363,898,924]" journalOrPublisher="Memorie del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale, Verona, Series 2, Sezione Science della Vita" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" pagination="1 - 150" part="2" refString="Ledoyer M. 1979. Les Gammariens de la pente externe du grand recif de Tulear (Madagascar). Memorie del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale, Verona, Series 2, Sezione Science della Vita 2: 1 - 150." title="Les Gammariens de la pente externe du grand recif de Tulear (Madagascar)" type="journal article" year="1979">Ledoyer 1979</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Ledoyer M." box="[377,436,898,924]" journalOrPublisher="Faune de Madagascar" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" pagination="599 - 1112" part="59" refString="Ledoyer M. 1986. Crustaces amphipodes gammariens. Faune de Madagascar 59 (2): 599 - 1112." title="Crustaces amphipodes gammariens" type="journal article" year="1986">1986</bibRefCitation>
